name: 3-in-1 Magnetic Wireless Charger Compatible with iPhone 16/15/14/All Series, Apple Watch, QI-Enabled Android, Magsafe Fast Charging Dock, Tri-Folding Bracket, Glacier White
description: The True Magnetic Wireless Charger: Tired of constantly plugging and unplugging charging cables? Switching to wireless charging is a great option. The night light offers a soft, adjustable brightness that won't disturb your sleep, and it features a memory function, so you won't need to adjust it repeatedly. Additionally, this charging dock stand is sleek and stylish, supporting both horizontal and vertical charging, and takes up very little space on your desk. It's perfect for your nightstand, vanity, office desk, or bathroom counter     Comprehensive Safety and Reliable Performance: Our 3-in-1 magnetic wireless fast charger features advanced overcurrent protection, overcharge protection, and reset protection. The concealed array of cooling vents ensures low-temperature charging, protecting your battery and giving you peace of mind, even when charging overnight     Package List: It supports phone output parameters of 15W (MAX)/10W/7.5W/5W, watch output of 5W (MAX), and earphone output of 5W (MAX). It’s lightweight and convenient for effortless portability     Customer Service You Can Rely On: Rest assured, every product we send goes through a comprehensive quality inspection process. If you have any questions about the wireless charging station, please contact us, and we will provide the best solution within 24 hours     Warning: Do not place metal debris or magnetic cards on the charging pad, as this may trigger the charger’s overheat alarm! Mild heating is normal, as phone batteries may warm up during charging. Do not place the charger near fire sources or in corrosive environments
